Team,

I have several custom extractors that are not showing up in Heritrix after
rebuild.  I double checked to make sure everything is in the right place --
.java files in ~/heritrix/src/java/org/archive/crawler/extractor folder,
Processor.options in the ~/heritrix/src/conf/modules, and profiles
directory in ~/heritrix/src/conf.

I get no errors but they are not included in the extractor selection.

What did I miss?

Thanks in advance.

David

--0016e6d7e94be727ea04be2d007c
